trans-unit.source:
Chrome filesystem is not immediately ready after device ready event. As a workaround you can subscribe to <code>filePluginIsReady</code> event. Example: <code>javascript
window.addEventListener('filePluginIsReady', function(){ console.log('File plugin is ready');}, false);
</code> You can use <code>window.isFilePluginReadyRaised</code> function to check whether event was already raised.
